      "answer": "c",
      "explanation": "Expand using powers of 2: 101101₂ = (1×2⁵) + (0×2⁴) + (1×2³) + (1×2²) + (0×2¹) + (1×2⁰) = 32 + 0 + 8 + 4 + 0 + 1 = 45"
