      "explanation": "Use division by 2: 39 ÷ 2 = 19 r1; 19 ÷ 2 = 9 r1; 9 ÷ 2 = 4 r1; 4 ÷ 2 = 2 r0; 2 ÷ 2 = 1 r0; 1 ÷ 2 = 0 r1. Read remainders from bottom to top: 100111₂"
    },

